N2  - The editorial continues several discussions begun in an earlier issue of Academy of Management Journal. The editor notes the inclusion of an index of book reviews included in this issue and discusses the idea of quarterly issue themes and announces the themes for the June and September issues. Further discussion about Academy of Management purpose, goals, and values is provided.
